eam/apps/1811940/extras/d00d003589a38fd8d27b4a073f1b0f5c.webp?t=1642182698\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811940/extras/d00d003589a38fd8d27b4a073f1b0f5c.poster.avif?t=1642182698\" class=\"bb_img\" width=546 height=540 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage your income</h2><br>Archipelago is all about risk/reward. Units must be paid a salary every wave. Play it safe with a lot of units, or take a risk with a few units but a higher income.",
